.= ( ( comp K ) . ( M1 * (i,j) ) ) by VECTSP_1:def 13
.= ( ( comp K ) . ( ( - p ) . ( ( ( j - i ) mod ( len p ) ) + 1 ) ) ) by A3,A1,A5,A14,A15,CKB68:def 1
